</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>/dev/disk0s2 on / <span class="o">(</span>hfs, <span class="nb">local</span>, journaled, noatime<span class="o">)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

